Steam’s latest Winter Sale is almost at an end, with a range of games on offer at discounted prices. The sale concludes on 3 January 2019 at 20:00, and PC gamers with cash left over after Christmas can buy many titles. Users can also access free digital items from Steam by clicking on the platform’s advent calendar page. This page displays a number of doors which open to reveal the digital items. The doors also feature art from a range of games. Among the titles on sale are Steam’s “top sellers” – games which are the most popular on the platform. The titles below are from this category and are available at discounted prices.         